com.att.cso.opendxl.jython.client

Class DxlMessage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.att.cso.opendxl.jython.client.DxlMessage

  • public class DxlMessage
extends java.lang.Object
    Message class to hold the fields of a OpenDXL message. This structure is used by the Python classes to send the data to the Java callback class that processes the OpenDXL message.
